{"search_data": "KarnatakaGas Bhagya Scheme in Karnataka for Free Gas Connections to BPL FamiliesKarnataka Government had earlier launched such scheme to distribute the free LPG connections to those who get their quota of Karosene from fair price shops. But, under the new Gas Bhagya scheme, free LPG connections will be given to those relying on firewood, crop residue or cowdung cake to cook."}